title: WTB: T206 Low Grade Common Lot
author: eliotdeutsch

posts.post_title: WTB: T206 Low Grade Common Lot
posts.post_content:
I’m afraid I’m staring at an eclipse. 
I know this might have negative long term consequences for my bank account - but I just can’t avert my eyes. 

For some reason I’ve caught the bug to try to tackle the monster. 
I think I want to start with a large lot of low grade commons. 

I’m afraid to go all in on HOFs now. 

So. If anyone has large lots of low grade, less rare backs to get me started, please PM me. 

I want to see how quickly, cheaply and easily I can acquire these. 

Prefer raw for these ones. 

Thanks.

Thinking about starting with T205 instead? 
Looks more doable?
